00a319 three course \\u2018Bouchon Menu\\u2019, changing weekly Monday to Friday, available until 7pm. New to 2015, Bar Boulud is now serving Sunday brunch from 11am to 3.30pm at \\u00a339.\",\"post_title\":\"Bar Boloud\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"open\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"bar-boloud\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"\",\"menu_order\":0,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":460,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2015-08-15 11:46:59\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2015-08-15 11:46:59\",\"post_content\":\"The Quarter Bar &amp; Lounge, opened in May 2011, sits at the heart of the redevelopment of the London Bridge Quarter.\\r\\n\\r\\nRelaxed and comfortable with a chic, contemporary atmosphere, Quarter Bar &amp; Lounge seats up to 70 people.\\r\\n\\r\\nServing social food ideal for relaxed conversations and meetings, menu choices range from a wide selection of platters (English cheeses, Italian, Indian &amp; Asian) to small dishes of vegetarian, fish, seafood and meat options - perfect for sharing.\\r\\n\\r\\nPerennial favourites such as cakes and pastries, sandwiches and salads, will be served, alongside Quarter Bar\'s very own beef burger, Club Sandwich and Afternoon Tea.\\r\\n\\r\\nCome the cocktail hour, the classics come into prominence (Cosmopolitan, Whisky Sour, Mojito, Side Car etc.), side by side with champagne cocktails and seasonally changed specials, taking inspiration from the fresh, market produce of nearby Borough Market - London\'s most famous gastronomic oasis.\\r\\n\\r\\nA full bar is of course available with soft drinks, a range of Tea Fort\\u00e9 teas, hot chocolate and coffees served by specially trained baristas.\",\"post_title\":\"Quarter Bar & Lounge\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"open\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"quarter-bar-lounge\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"\",\"menu_order\":0,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":441,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2015-06-17 10:38:05\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2015-10-22 13:03:15\",\"post_content\":\"Welcome to the Lounge at W London, the hottest place to see and be seen. Sip inventive cocktails mixed to perfection in a pulsating lounge atmosphere, and mingle and socialise over the vibrant tunes of our up-and-coming DJs.\\r\\n\\r\\nDuring the day, enjoy a playful and exotic twist on the quintessentially British afternoon tea, the \'W Spice Tea\'.\\r\\n\\r\\nEvery Sunday, slip into the lounge for \'W Does Brunch\': the experience fuses classic sitcoms in the private screening room, chilled music by resident DJ and professional show-off Anna Greenwood, and delicious food, creating the ideal way to round off a busy weekend in the capital.\\r\\n\\r\\nDrink. Dance. Lounge.\",\"post_title\":\"W Lounge\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"open\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"w-lounge\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"\",\"menu_order\":0,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":606,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2015-04-16 15:29:42\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2015-10-23 08:46:29\",\"post_content\":\"Located in 12 converted Georgian townhouses around a central courtyard, this budget boutique hotel is a 3-minute walk from Leicester Square Underground Station, a 6-minute walk from the <span class=\\\"_dgc kd-hc\\\" data-ved=\\\"0CM4BENxNMA5qFQoTCN_D09eY2MgCFUJUGgodQp8FZQ\\\"><span class=\\\"_J5e\\\">National Portrait Gallery and an 8-minute walk from Piccadilly Circus.<\\/span><\\/span>\\r\\n\\r\\nSimple, contemporary rooms feature free WiFi and flat-screen TVs with cable channels; some lack windows.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe on-site cafe serves breakfast, snacks and drinks.\",\"post_title\":\"The Z Hotel Soho\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"open\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"the-z-hotel-soho\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2018-03-09 07:20:19\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"\",\"menu_order\":0,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":622,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2015-03-27 11:47:48\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2015-10-23 09:14:57\",\"post_content\":\"With venues in both Mayfair and Knightsbridge, Mamounia Lounge allows guests to enjoy a truly authentic Arabic drinking and dining experience in the heart of London.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe restaurants\\u2019 Middle Eastern menu features the very best of traditional Lebanese and Moroccan cuisines aswell as a selection of European fusion dishes created by their experienced head chefs, whilst an eclectic cocktail list is served at the bars by expert mixologists.\\r\\n\\r\\nPerfect for relaxed day-time dining, at night both venues come alive with beautiful belly-dancers, and traditional Middle Eastern musicians, evoking the energetic buzz of Marrakech, for an unforgettable experience every time.\",\"post_title\":\"Mamounia Lounge\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"open\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"mamounia-lounge\",\"t